TCD 2.0:
Now works with gtk 0.99.5 and up.

Some very nice icon sets by Charles Sielski! Check out Bevel and SmallBlack.

Not much new stuff..nearing release quality.

TCD 2.0b2:
Tooltips. ./configure --enable-notooltips if you don't want them.

Added a kind of a theme support. Check icons/README.

Switched to GNU autoconf. If you have problems:

	cp Makefile.old Makefile
	make normal
	make install

Bug fixes
You can hide everything but the time display by right clicking on it.
Left & Right click on the current track display to switch tracks.

TCD 2.0b:

New track database format.
Gtk+ interface!
